OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain, heavy at times, especially over
OL,7,Fwestern hills, will move quickly
OL,8,Feastwards across all areas this
OL,9,Fevening. This clearing during the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Wednesday morning,
OL,11,Fafter which it will become dry with
OL,12,Fsome clear spells. Windy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA rather blustery day, with
OL,15,Fa mixture of sunny spells and showers.
OL,16,FThe showers are likely to be heavy at
OL,17,Ftimes, especially on western hills.
OL,18,FStaying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
