OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fband of rain, locally heavy, moves
OL,7,Ferratically southeastwards Thursday,
OL,8,Faccompanied by squally winds. Colder
OL,9,Fon Friday, with sunny spells and
OL,10,Fblustery showers. Drier, brighter and
OL,11,Fless windy on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
